## Posting Frequency

- **Minimum:** 3 posts/week to stay algorithm-active
- **Optimal:** 4–5 posts/week during active job search or client acquisition
- **Suggested weekly mix:**
  - Mon: Authority post (case study or opinion)
  - Wed: Authority post (process breakdown or how-to)
  - Fri: Visibility or personal post (story, behind-the-scenes)
  - Thu optional (max 1× per 2 weeks): Conversion post

